burger-monger.name: Burger Monger
burger-monger.description: Local counter-serve chain featuring burgers, fries & malts, plus beer & wine, in a casual space.

five-guys.name: Five Guys
five-guys.description: Fast-food chain with made-to-order burgers, fries & hot dogs, plus free peanuts while you wait.

bjs-brewhouse.name: BJ's Brewhouse
bjs-brewhouse.description: Family-friendly chain outpost pairs familiar pub fare with an extensive list of house brews.

pollo-tropical.name: Pollo Tropical
pollo-tropical.description: Counter-serve chain for Caribbean grilled chicken & pork platters, sandwiches & more.

glory-days.name: Glory Days
glory-days.description: Sports-bar chain featuring hearty American fare (including gluten-free dishes) & games on TV.

cheddars.name: Cheddars
cheddars.description: Family-friendly chain serving American comfort food with a Texas twist, plus cocktails.

pei-wei.name: Pei Wei
pei-wei.description: Counter-serve Pan-Asian chain for health-conscious noodle & rice dishes & more.

ale-house.name: Ale House
ale-house.description: Casual sports-pub chain with basics from bar snacks to steaks & a large selection of tap beers.

casual-clam.name: Casual Clam
casual-clam.description: Low-key seafood joint offering classic fish 'n' chips & lobster rolls, plus pastas & plate dinners.

bonefish-grill.name: BoneFish Grill
bonefish-grill.description: Contemporary grill chain offering a seafood-centric menu, plus steaks & cocktails.
